egory:Aerospace business development agencies]]\n[[Category:State agencies of New Mexico]]\n", "name_user": "TheLabyrinthMaker", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Mexico_Spaceport_Authority"}
